c: 48
v: 15
t: "Abo babeshiyeke ngemva baza kuthi xa nisiya kuthabatha ixhayelo; “Masinilandele nathi.” Banqwenela ukuguqula amazwi ka-Allâh. Yithi: “Aningekhe\tnisilandele. Sele\tEtsho njalo\tuAllâh kwangaphambili” Baya kuthi ke bona: “Nini nje abasimonelayo”\tkodwa\t(enyanisweni)\tbabengaqiqi\tnto ngaphandle kokuncinane"